entry.name: PBC-DIGE
entry.description:
DIGE combined with MALDI-TOF-TOF MS/MS was applied to explore the differential expressed proteins between AMA positive and negative PBC.
NB Extra peak files are available on the FTP for this project .

additional_fields.field: Immunoaffinity depletion of high abundant serum proteins; protein labeling.
DIGE analysis; Identification of statistically different spots between groups.
No PTMs are included in the dataset
